    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-6cb459a6-1e43-40fe-820a-9b0a4eeb243d">
                Mr. Granville
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-6cb459a6-1e43-40fe-820a-9b0a4eeb243d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-03-12/debates/eee78343-48cc-4787-a3b2-b0006c4bc073/UnitedStatesLease-LendBill#contribution-6cb459a6-1e43-40fe-820a-9b0a4eeb243d">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">May I ask the Prime Minister, in view of the great importance of this statement whether he would consider making a broadcast to the United States of America in similar terms and on a wavelength which could be heard by the people of this country as well?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-6cb459a6-1e43-40fe-820a-9b0a4eeb243d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1941-03-12/debates/eee78343-48cc-4787-a3b2-b0006c4bc073/UnitedStatesLease-LendBill#contribution-6cb459a6-1e43-40fe-820a-9b0a4eeb243d">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-e9f67ac8-1d5a-4bae-9ac2-9e7654190605">
